.vite/

# SQLite WAL/SHM sidecars. Transient — SQLite creates them next to a DB
# opened in WAL mode. Our bundled DBs open read-only (mode=ro&immutable=1)
# so these shouldn't appear, but catch them anyway in case someone opens
# a local copy for ad-hoc write-mode refreshes.
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.db-journal

